ur measurements in the context of\nprevious work in the literature, which reported considerably longer lifetimes\nfor molecular clouds in the LMC, and find that these previous findings resulted\nfrom a subjective choice in timeline calibration that is avoided by our\nstatistical methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 18:38:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-28"}
