$, respectively. We highlight\nthat the Arnett model, Arnett's rule, and hydrodynamical models typically\noverestimate the $^{56}$Ni masses of SE SNe by 75, 90 and 65%, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2022 19:06:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
