unistic scheme in both scenarios can achieve higher\ncommunication performance for NOMA than the baseline schemes merely employing\nSemCom or BitCom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 13:52:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
