 error in the manual tag installation process and propose a\nstochastic approach to account for this uncertainty using the Lie group theory.\nEmploying Monte Carlo simulation, we experimentally show that the proposed\nstochastic model incorporated in our on-manifold formulation improves the\nrobustness and accuracy of tag-based localization against inevitable\nimperfections in manual tag installation on site.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 15:01:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
