arge-scale manufacturing capability, and cost-effective, and can be a strong\ncandidate for THz light-matter interaction platform.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 15:22:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-25"}
